Dashboard redesign preview patch
================================

Status: REVIEW ONLY. This file is for design/implementation review and has not been
applied to the working tree.

Important implementation decisions included here:
- Keep `--navy-deep:#141b32` intact for landing/button hover.
- Add `--navy-sidebar:#151c33` for the dashboard sidebar.
- Add sage/ready tokens and expose them in Tailwind.
- Add Button `sage` variant.
- Implement Style/Count as keyboard-accessible radio groups with roving tabindex and
  ArrowLeft/ArrowRight/ArrowUp/ArrowDown handling, avoiding a Radix install for now.
- Keep TaskPill local to `/dashboard/headshots` for this pass because there is no
  `app/(dashboard)/layout.tsx` and no additional real route under `/dashboard` yet.
  TODO remains in the component to lift it to a provider when dashboard routes grow.

